 ures intricate carvings and stunning architecture. The monument is a testa
 ment to the rich history and culture of Jodhpur.\n  → Transport: Hire an
  auto-rickshaw from the hotel for ₹100\, 20-minute ride\n- 11:00 🚂 De
 parture: Jodhpur Railway Station — Take the train from Jodhpur to Mumbai
